WEBVTT

01:51.920 --> 01:57.390
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.520 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 31]

02:04.610 --> 02:05.460
Tian Xing,

02:05.490 --> 02:06.420
take these over.

02:10.430 --> 02:11.360
Here, Suyin.

02:12.810 --> 02:14.900
This is a kind of pastry
unique to Jing City,

02:14.900 --> 02:16.060
called "Reunion Cake."

02:16.060 --> 02:19.460
It's specially made for
the Autumn Moon Festival every year.

02:20.020 --> 02:20.940
I didn't expect

02:20.940 --> 02:23.130
Jing City to have such delicate customs.

02:23.130 --> 02:23.850
Yeah.

02:23.850 --> 02:25.250
Just like I used to think

02:25.250 --> 02:27.220
people in Jing City were all
martial and aggressive.

02:27.220 --> 02:28.570
I never expected there to be

02:28.570 --> 02:31.430
such gentle and kind-hearted people
here, either.

02:37.970 --> 02:38.740
Gao Ran.

02:39.570 --> 02:41.260
About us going to Jing City,

02:41.410 --> 02:43.110
you haven't told my father yet, right?

02:43.110 --> 02:45.130
Lord Fan Qi has been off duty
and resting at home these past few days.

02:45.130 --> 02:46.790
He probably doesn't know yet.

02:47.570 --> 02:48.300
Then...

02:49.250 --> 02:50.300
Then let's do this.

02:50.300 --> 02:51.130
Don't tell

02:51.410 --> 02:52.780
Dad just yet.

02:53.740 --> 02:56.140
Let's just enjoy the Autumn Moon Festival.

02:56.140 --> 02:57.420
I'll find a chance later

02:57.420 --> 02:58.980
to talk to him properly.

02:59.810 --> 03:00.460
I agree.

03:05.620 --> 03:07.020
Are we expecting guests?

03:07.530 --> 03:09.660
Probably someone Lord Fan Qi invited.

03:10.740 --> 03:11.940
What brings you here?

03:23.890 --> 03:25.760
Governor, what are you

03:25.780 --> 03:27.040
holding in your hands?

03:35.250 --> 03:37.250
Let me formally introduce it to you.

03:37.410 --> 03:40.620
This is a special Autumn Moon Festival
offering from Gao City.

03:40.620 --> 03:42.300
I haven't had the chance to study it yet.

03:42.300 --> 03:43.220
It's said that

03:43.220 --> 03:44.550
if you place it in a room,

03:44.620 --> 03:46.060
it can freshen the air.

03:46.960 --> 03:47.960
Your Excellency.

03:48.340 --> 03:49.940
This fruit is called pomelo.

03:50.300 --> 03:52.829
It's a close relative
of the mandarin orange,

03:53.740 --> 03:55.340
but its flavor

03:55.340 --> 03:57.460
is even sweeter and more refreshing
than that of a mandarin.

03:57.460 --> 04:00.250
Eating it moistens the lungs
and relieves dryness,

04:00.250 --> 04:01.680
and even just smelling it

04:02.130 --> 04:04.330
gives off a pleasant, fresh fragrance.

04:04.780 --> 04:07.110
You truly are knowledgeable, Lord Fan Qi.

04:07.540 --> 04:09.250
I could tell this item was extraordinary,

04:09.250 --> 04:11.180
so I specifically brought it over
for Lady Fan Yun—

04:11.180 --> 04:12.810
someone who appreciates the finer things
both in life and romance—

04:12.810 --> 04:13.670
to have a taste.

04:14.300 --> 04:15.730
Thank you, Your Excellency,

04:15.730 --> 04:16.940
for giving us

04:16.970 --> 04:19.589
such a wonderful gift.

04:20.100 --> 04:23.270
I'll go chill it in well water right away,

04:23.300 --> 04:24.940
and we'll all enjoy it together later

04:24.940 --> 04:26.500
when we admire the moon.

04:27.450 --> 04:28.180
Thank you, Father.

04:28.180 --> 04:29.910
Thank you for the trouble then.

04:30.340 --> 04:31.070
Be careful.

04:37.300 --> 04:37.980
Governor.

04:38.000 --> 04:39.730
Today is the Reunion Festival.

04:40.130 --> 04:41.770
Is there no banquet in your mansion?

04:41.770 --> 04:42.570
Don't tell me

04:43.130 --> 04:44.730
you sneaked over here again.

04:47.010 --> 04:48.659
Like you said, it's the Reunion Festival.

04:48.659 --> 04:49.740
So of course you should spend it
with your family

04:49.740 --> 04:51.570
for it to count as a reunion.

04:51.940 --> 04:52.659
I

04:52.770 --> 04:54.100
have already sent
all the attendants and maids

04:54.100 --> 04:56.810
in the mansion home for the holiday.

04:57.470 --> 04:59.400
And now that everyone's gone home,

04:59.659 --> 05:02.070
I was the only one left in the mansion,

05:02.200 --> 05:03.150
all alone.

05:03.810 --> 05:04.860
That's why...

05:05.460 --> 05:06.090
Fan Yun.

05:06.540 --> 05:07.560
It's a festival, after all.

05:07.560 --> 05:08.960
Let His Excellency stay.

05:11.570 --> 05:12.210
It's okay.

05:13.400 --> 05:14.960
It's your family reunion.

05:15.020 --> 05:15.830
I...

05:16.370 --> 05:17.900
I won't bother you further.

05:18.210 --> 05:19.010
Your Excellency...

05:19.010 --> 05:20.070
Enjoy yourselves.

05:26.070 --> 05:27.620
You didn't even try to stop me.

05:27.620 --> 05:29.300
I didn't ask you to leave
in the first place.

05:29.300 --> 05:30.650
I knew it.

05:30.940 --> 05:32.050
We are family, after all,

05:32.050 --> 05:32.620
right?

05:33.060 --> 05:34.010
We used to be.

05:34.450 --> 05:35.500
Once married...

05:36.159 --> 05:37.610
Shut your mouth.

05:38.450 --> 05:39.650
Don't talk nonsense.

05:40.130 --> 05:41.860
This tofu is really delicious.

06:03.990 --> 06:04.840
Look,

06:04.960 --> 06:06.090
that little sapling

06:06.750 --> 06:07.880
has grown so much.

06:13.790 --> 06:14.610
Yeah.

06:15.400 --> 06:16.740
As long as it's placed
in the right environment,

06:16.740 --> 06:17.940
it will grow quickly.

06:18.440 --> 06:20.300
These saplings are just like you.

06:24.930 --> 06:28.100
It's been a while
since I last had Yun's cooking.

06:30.100 --> 06:31.100
It's really delicious.

06:31.100 --> 06:33.300
Just thinking about it makes me hungry.

06:35.370 --> 06:36.220
Absolutely.

06:36.540 --> 06:38.740
Fan Yun's cooking is indeed excellent.

06:41.210 --> 06:42.159
It's just

06:42.200 --> 06:44.400
a bit of a shame to think
I won't be able to

06:46.700 --> 06:48.360
enjoy her cooking for a while.

06:53.640 --> 06:54.760
Your Excellency.

06:54.980 --> 06:56.810
Isn't Yun's cooking something

06:56.810 --> 06:58.790
you can have whenever you want?

06:59.010 --> 07:00.330
How come

07:00.330 --> 07:02.530
you won't be able to enjoy it for a while?

07:03.770 --> 07:04.810
-You have no idea...
-Here's the thing,

07:04.810 --> 07:05.690
Dad.

07:06.610 --> 07:08.610
From today onwards,

07:08.640 --> 07:10.740
I'll be quite busy with official duties.

07:10.740 --> 07:11.570
So

07:11.570 --> 07:13.100
I won't have much time

07:13.100 --> 07:14.330
to cook delicious meals.

07:14.330 --> 07:15.790
-Yeah, yeah.
-That's why.

07:17.110 --> 07:17.940
Right. Right.

07:17.940 --> 07:19.620
I haven't had the chance to ask you yet.

07:19.620 --> 07:22.940
Were you ultimately assigned to
the Commerce Bureau

07:22.940 --> 07:24.300
or the Affairs Bureau?

07:25.540 --> 07:26.200
A... Aff...

07:32.370 --> 07:33.500
The Affairs Bureau.

07:34.250 --> 07:35.100
Well, the Affairs Bureau...

07:35.100 --> 07:36.210
No, I said it wrong.

07:37.060 --> 07:38.100
It's...

07:40.420 --> 07:41.250
It's the Commerce Bureau.

07:41.250 --> 07:42.350
The Commerce Bureau...

07:42.350 --> 07:43.590
No, not that either.

07:44.690 --> 07:45.370
It is...

07:46.450 --> 07:47.210
It is...

07:48.100 --> 07:49.130
So what is it exactly?

07:49.130 --> 07:50.420
Lord Fan Qi.

07:50.420 --> 07:51.570
We don't often get holidays like this.

07:51.570 --> 07:53.830
Let's not talk about official business.

07:54.909 --> 07:56.030
Yes, Dad.

07:56.060 --> 07:56.890
Have some fruit.

07:56.890 --> 07:57.820
Here. Have some.

08:00.180 --> 08:01.450
Why do I feel like

08:02.420 --> 08:04.550
you guys are hiding something from me?

08:05.050 --> 08:06.250
-Well...
-We aren't.

08:06.370 --> 08:07.690
How could we?

08:07.710 --> 08:09.430
What could we possibly

08:09.770 --> 08:11.450
dare to hide from you, Dad?

08:12.910 --> 08:14.290
Don't tell me you two haven't...

08:14.290 --> 08:16.420
We haven't got to taste the pomelo yet.

08:17.060 --> 08:18.060
Your Excellency.

08:18.740 --> 08:20.330
What exactly is this about?

08:22.130 --> 08:22.620
I just wanted to say...

08:22.620 --> 08:25.420
-Governor!
-Your Excellency, have a taste first.

08:28.700 --> 08:29.500
Is it sweet?

08:33.780 --> 08:36.090
Why haven't you been
talking to me tonight?

08:36.090 --> 08:36.900
Besides,

08:36.900 --> 08:39.500
this matter can't be kept
under wraps forever.

08:39.870 --> 08:41.559
-Your Excellency?
-Governor.

08:41.559 --> 08:43.760
Look, it's getting late.

08:43.809 --> 08:45.300
You've been out of the mansion
for quite a while now.

08:45.300 --> 08:46.420
It's time for you to go back and rest.

08:46.420 --> 08:47.690
Your Excellency.

08:47.690 --> 08:50.200
What is it that can't be kept under wraps?

09:00.740 --> 09:01.140
I...

09:01.170 --> 09:02.100
Dad!

09:03.450 --> 09:04.300
Come on and take a look.

09:04.300 --> 09:08.360
-Gao Ran's hand is having an allergic reaction.
-Bring him the medicine!

09:09.570 --> 09:12.060
Your Excellency, what is it?

09:17.710 --> 09:18.350
I...

09:18.370 --> 09:19.130
I...

09:19.160 --> 09:21.000
have already promised...

09:21.420 --> 09:22.490
-Fan Yun...
-Dad.

09:25.970 --> 09:27.060
I'll tell you.

09:33.490 --> 09:34.420
Actually,

09:36.180 --> 09:37.140
next,

09:38.450 --> 09:40.420
I'm neither going to the Affairs Bureau

09:40.420 --> 09:41.820
nor the Commerce Bureau,

09:49.140 --> 09:50.380
but to Jing City.

09:59.450 --> 10:02.060
Zheng Xian, come here.

10:03.810 --> 10:05.450
I have something to tell you.

10:06.090 --> 10:06.890
Grandfather,

10:07.210 --> 10:08.810
what are your instructions?

10:09.730 --> 10:12.020
Zheng Shi is returning to Jing City.

10:12.490 --> 10:14.450
You must keep a close eye on him.

10:15.020 --> 10:16.170
You want me to go back?

10:16.170 --> 10:17.300
Then what about you?

10:19.610 --> 10:22.570
The governor is now suspicious of me,

10:24.660 --> 10:28.020
and I've made another misstep
regarding the position of gate commander.

10:28.020 --> 10:29.210
Qi Zheng will definitely

10:29.210 --> 10:31.540
try to stop me from
returning to Jing City.

10:31.690 --> 10:34.020
Now is not the time
to fall out with him yet.

10:34.380 --> 10:36.210
If he insists on keeping me here,

10:36.970 --> 10:38.490
I'll stay.

10:40.730 --> 10:42.060
Then I'll stay with you.

10:45.730 --> 10:47.380
Silly boy.

10:47.900 --> 10:48.810
If Zheng Shi goes back

10:48.810 --> 10:50.130
and you don't,

10:50.730 --> 10:55.160
wouldn't that be like handing the position
of clan leader to him on a silver platter?

10:55.160 --> 10:56.920
So you mean

10:57.060 --> 10:59.060
you want me to go back
and take up the position of clan leader?

10:59.060 --> 11:00.850
After you go back,
be sure to do everything you can

11:00.850 --> 11:04.300
to support Zheng Jin
in becoming the clan leader.

11:07.180 --> 11:08.090
Okay.

11:10.850 --> 11:13.930
Zheng Shi is unpredictable
and deeply scheming.

11:14.210 --> 11:16.060
I'm worried that this time,

11:16.900 --> 11:18.330
while he's ostensibly returning

11:18.330 --> 11:21.340
to bring back your Granduncle's ashes,

11:22.810 --> 11:24.810
he's actually setting his sights on

11:25.260 --> 11:26.860
the clan leader's position.

11:29.260 --> 11:31.210
With the whereabouts of
the clan leader ring unknown,

11:31.210 --> 11:32.550
I feel uneasy.

11:36.630 --> 11:38.840
Zheng Jin is straightforward,

11:38.940 --> 11:41.180
and you, Zheng Xian, are simple-minded.

11:41.180 --> 11:43.020
Neither of you is a match for him.

11:43.490 --> 11:46.450
Only if you two brothers work together

11:46.940 --> 11:49.060
can you have a chance of success.

11:51.330 --> 11:53.060
But Zheng Shi never said

11:53.060 --> 11:55.260
he wanted to be the clan leader himself.

11:56.260 --> 11:57.850
Silly boy.

12:03.450 --> 12:05.180
Just because he doesn't say it,

12:05.260 --> 12:07.520
does that mean he has no such intentions?

12:08.570 --> 12:11.110
Then what do you make of

12:11.610 --> 12:14.470
him favoring the Fan family girl
as gate commander?

12:14.780 --> 12:16.970
You must follow my instructions
on this matter.

12:16.970 --> 12:19.220
Absolutely do not act on your own.

12:19.450 --> 12:20.540
Remember this—

12:22.180 --> 12:25.020
you must not drift apart from Zheng Jin.

12:27.390 --> 12:29.320
Okay. I'll do as you say.

12:42.090 --> 12:43.520
Since you saw me,

12:43.850 --> 12:45.250
why didn't you come over?

13:03.420 --> 13:05.750
I saw you enjoying the lake view,
Miss Wei,

13:06.090 --> 13:07.820
so I didn't want to disturb you.

13:09.540 --> 13:10.540
I was thinking,

13:11.300 --> 13:13.020
could there be at least once when,

13:13.020 --> 13:14.330
at the moment of parting,

13:14.330 --> 13:16.260
you're the one who comes to find me?

13:17.140 --> 13:18.380
Maybe this time,

13:18.690 --> 13:20.150
could you take me with you?

13:21.180 --> 13:22.330
No.

13:22.330 --> 13:23.660
This time is different.

13:25.810 --> 13:27.180
Actually, I already guessed.

13:27.180 --> 13:28.490
I just wanted to try and see

13:28.490 --> 13:30.550
if there would be a different answer.

13:31.420 --> 13:32.410
As expected.

13:35.490 --> 13:36.780
Honestly,

13:36.780 --> 13:38.060
since you're always hustling around
out there,

13:38.060 --> 13:40.460
there's really not much I can do
to help you.

13:40.660 --> 13:41.850
I just want

13:42.300 --> 13:44.630
to do whatever little I can
to support you.

13:46.450 --> 13:48.510
Then what if I'm not hustling around?

13:51.660 --> 13:53.140
Just the thought of

13:53.140 --> 13:55.070
not seeing you for a long time again

13:55.380 --> 13:56.330
makes me…

14:05.450 --> 14:06.730
It would be nice to have an amulet with me

14:06.730 --> 14:08.970
when I'm away from home.

14:11.940 --> 14:12.900
An amulet?

14:12.900 --> 14:14.420
You've started believing in that too?

14:14.420 --> 14:16.850
It's better to believe it than not.

14:16.850 --> 14:18.380
Don't underestimate yourself.

14:18.380 --> 14:20.260
Besides, the help you gave me before

14:20.260 --> 14:21.590
really meant a lot to me.

14:21.730 --> 14:24.260
Then, does this count as

14:24.260 --> 14:25.520
your validation of me?

14:31.300 --> 14:33.430
It's my validation of your intuition.

14:37.330 --> 14:38.330
Come back soon.

14:38.330 --> 14:40.060
Don't keep me waiting too long.

15:49.850 --> 15:51.060
Your Excellency.

15:52.940 --> 15:53.850
Lord Fan Qi.

15:57.450 --> 15:58.540
I heard from Fan Yun

15:59.090 --> 16:01.570
that you usually visit your wife's grave
on her birthday

16:01.570 --> 16:03.690
rather than on
the anniversary of her death.

16:03.690 --> 16:05.020
So I came here early this morning

16:05.020 --> 16:06.420
to wait for you.

16:08.300 --> 16:09.630
I never want to remember

16:09.690 --> 16:11.360
the days of parting.

16:17.020 --> 16:17.850
I understand.

16:25.060 --> 16:27.450
I won't let Fan Yun disobey your order.

16:29.090 --> 16:32.290
But I'm sure you feel reluctant
to part with her deep down.

16:33.570 --> 16:36.450
We are both Your Excellency's subjects.

16:37.690 --> 16:38.610
But Fan Yun

16:39.770 --> 16:41.770
is my only daughter.

16:45.490 --> 16:46.420
In my heart,

16:47.850 --> 16:50.180
Fan Yun is different from other subjects.

16:51.570 --> 16:53.620
Regardless of our current status,

16:54.090 --> 16:55.210
in my heart,

16:55.730 --> 16:57.390
Fan Yun's always been my wife.

16:58.300 --> 17:01.100
I won't let her go off
on a dangerous journey alone.

17:02.190 --> 17:03.300
There's something

17:03.730 --> 17:05.329
that shouldn't be revealed,

17:05.420 --> 17:07.950
but I feel that
only if you put your mind at ease

17:08.450 --> 17:12.250
will Fan Yun be able to go to Jing City
without any lingering worries.

17:16.730 --> 17:17.940
What is this?

17:18.530 --> 17:21.069
This is a headband I obtained
from the Sacred Rites Bureau.

17:21.069 --> 17:23.210
It has the power
to change one's appearance.

17:23.210 --> 17:25.069
I've discussed this with Gao Ran—

17:25.859 --> 17:27.460
I'll disguise myself as him

17:27.770 --> 17:29.230
and stay by Fan Yun's side.

17:30.050 --> 17:30.890
This way,

17:30.980 --> 17:32.180
you can rest assured.

17:32.770 --> 17:34.830
That only makes me even more worried.

17:34.900 --> 17:35.940
Your Excellency,

17:36.380 --> 17:38.840
your martial skills
can't even hold a candle

17:38.970 --> 17:41.380
to Gao Ran's.

17:42.660 --> 17:44.690
My devotion is second to none.

17:46.140 --> 17:47.900
But in times of emergency,

17:47.900 --> 17:51.180
you may have the will
but not the strength to act.

17:52.820 --> 17:54.680
Please rest assured, Lord Fan Qi.

17:55.180 --> 17:56.440
In times of emergency,

17:56.900 --> 17:59.230
I'll definitely protect her with my life.

18:01.050 --> 18:02.180
Your Excellency.

18:02.180 --> 18:04.770
I can see how much you care for Fan Yun.

18:05.900 --> 18:07.380
I have no qualms about

18:07.380 --> 18:09.420
entrusting Fan Yun to you.

18:16.450 --> 18:17.730
I also know

18:18.660 --> 18:20.660
what Your Excellency intends to do.

18:24.010 --> 18:24.970
May everything

18:26.100 --> 18:28.420
go smoothly and safely

18:28.420 --> 18:30.100
for you both.

18:33.300 --> 18:34.560
Thank you, Lord Fan Qi.

18:55.420 --> 18:57.050
Back then,

18:58.210 --> 19:00.810
you wanted to practice medicine
to save lives.

19:01.620 --> 19:02.670
And now,

19:03.970 --> 19:07.030
she wants to serve the people
as a government official.

19:09.940 --> 19:12.820
Both are for the good of the people.

19:13.530 --> 19:14.820
This is good.

19:15.450 --> 19:16.660
This is good.

19:19.450 --> 19:21.340
If this is

19:23.210 --> 19:24.880
the kind of person

19:25.380 --> 19:27.310
you wanted our daughter to become,

19:29.130 --> 19:31.850
then please watch over her for me

19:33.450 --> 19:34.580
and guard her

19:36.290 --> 19:38.000
from the heavens.

19:47.250 --> 19:49.210
Your daughter is here.

19:58.510 --> 19:59.910
Alright, show yourself.

20:20.830 --> 20:21.900
Dad.

20:32.370 --> 20:34.490
Make sure to make the most of

20:35.250 --> 20:37.580
the opportunity you've earned yourself.

20:40.820 --> 20:41.970
Don't bring shame on

20:42.450 --> 20:43.770
me and your mother.

20:50.040 --> 20:50.800
Dad,

20:51.690 --> 20:52.450
thank you.

21:16.010 --> 21:17.540
There's nothing wrong with

21:18.290 --> 21:19.820
Gao Ran dressing like this,

21:20.940 --> 21:21.620
but his posture feels

21:21.620 --> 21:23.350
a bit too stiff and restrained.

21:24.350 --> 21:26.610
Gao Ran, why don't you try relaxing a bit?

21:30.100 --> 21:31.210
According to
the Services Bureau's etiquette,

21:31.210 --> 21:32.450
when the governor is standing,

21:32.450 --> 21:34.210
the feet should be together,

21:34.580 --> 21:36.250
straight and orderly like a plant,

21:36.250 --> 21:39.140
the neck extended, head held up,
and hands naturally at rest.

21:39.140 --> 21:40.290
If I relax any more than that,

21:40.290 --> 21:42.620
it would be improper and against decorum.

21:43.610 --> 21:44.100
Um...

21:45.770 --> 21:47.370
Then try walking a few steps.

21:56.490 --> 21:57.150
Stop. Stop.

21:59.290 --> 22:01.000
This is way too stiff.

22:01.340 --> 22:02.800
Is that how I usually walk?

22:03.050 --> 22:04.490
As recorded in the "Nine Cities Canon,"

22:04.490 --> 22:05.770
when a governor walks,

22:05.970 --> 22:08.690
he should be dignified on the inside
and upright on the outside,

22:08.690 --> 22:11.010
without swaying from side to side,
and his movements measured and proper.

22:11.010 --> 22:12.890
Your usual way of walking, Governor,

22:12.890 --> 22:14.490
is really a bit undisciplined.

22:14.490 --> 22:15.180
But...

22:17.230 --> 22:18.190
I told you,

22:18.450 --> 22:21.230
Gao Ran looks more like a governor
than His Excellency himself.

22:21.230 --> 22:22.790
More accurately, it's that His Excellency

22:22.790 --> 22:24.720
just doesn't look like a governor.

22:24.890 --> 22:25.810
I think

22:25.860 --> 22:27.050
we can wrap up the course now.

22:27.050 --> 22:28.100
I haven't even left yet,
and you're already

22:28.100 --> 22:30.630
-Ouch! It hurts!
-starting a rebellion, huh?

22:32.090 --> 22:33.020
Oh well, oh well.

22:34.340 --> 22:35.670
What can I do? Our Gao Ran

22:36.010 --> 22:37.900
is naturally cut out to be a governor.

22:37.900 --> 22:39.180
See? See?

22:39.180 --> 22:40.540
Just this "oh well"

22:40.560 --> 22:42.820
is not something Gao Ran would say at all.

22:42.830 --> 22:45.620
Gao Ran is dignified and graceful
in his interactions with others.

22:45.620 --> 22:46.770
Compared to His Excellency,
he's definitely not as wild...

22:46.770 --> 22:48.290
Charming and dashing!

22:52.010 --> 22:52.690
Move aside.

22:55.450 --> 22:56.970
During morning assemblies,

22:56.970 --> 22:58.770
I do come across as dignified and serious.

22:58.770 --> 23:00.180
Gao Ran can imitate that part

23:00.180 --> 23:01.340
just fine.

23:02.210 --> 23:03.660
It's just in private settings—

23:03.660 --> 23:05.520
if anyone who knows me is present—

23:09.820 --> 23:11.940
that I'll need the two of you
to play along.

23:11.940 --> 23:14.070
Gao Ran only needs to respond briefly.

23:14.380 --> 23:15.310
Respond to what?

23:15.660 --> 23:17.260
It's simple. I'll teach you.

23:18.450 --> 23:19.180
You may rise.

23:20.050 --> 23:20.780
You may rise.

23:21.100 --> 23:21.730
Granted.

23:23.730 --> 23:24.350
Granted.

23:24.550 --> 23:25.470
You may leave!

23:25.790 --> 23:26.610
You may leave!

23:28.510 --> 23:29.460
Not bad, not bad.

23:29.530 --> 23:30.690
With just those few lines,

23:30.690 --> 23:32.420
you can't tell the difference.

23:32.820 --> 23:34.620
Your standards are way too low.

23:35.580 --> 23:36.820
You just need to practice more.

23:36.820 --> 23:39.080
It seems like you'll get there in no time.

23:39.690 --> 23:40.860
Don't blame me for saying this,

23:40.860 --> 23:41.750
but I really can't bring myself

23:41.750 --> 23:43.250
to cheer like that normally,

23:43.250 --> 23:44.690
especially in front of Fan Yun.

23:44.690 --> 23:46.090
You must not forget that.

23:49.180 --> 23:51.110
Then, Gao Ran, why don't you tell me

23:51.180 --> 23:53.510
how you usually communicate with Fan Yun?

23:55.580 --> 23:57.860
There's no fixed way of talking.

23:58.290 --> 24:00.180
Fan Yun has been lively and restless
since childhood,

24:00.180 --> 24:01.380
not very concerned with etiquette.

24:01.380 --> 24:03.450
I've basically just been
fulfilling my duty as a caregiver.

24:03.450 --> 24:05.010
Just act like an older brother

24:05.010 --> 24:06.050
and ask her things like

24:06.050 --> 24:06.940
whether she's eating well

24:06.940 --> 24:08.470
or dressed warmly enough.

24:08.840 --> 24:09.840
What else...

24:10.130 --> 24:10.780
Right.

24:11.580 --> 24:13.380
I rarely turn down her requests.

24:13.590 --> 24:15.450
Whatever she says, you just do it?

24:15.620 --> 24:18.620
Yeah. I don't often stop her
from doing what she wants.

24:20.750 --> 24:22.410
Well, as her "older brother,"

24:22.580 --> 24:23.910
you really do spoil her.

24:25.450 --> 24:26.210
Alright.

24:26.210 --> 24:27.450
As long as we keep these in mind,

24:27.450 --> 24:28.820
we shouldn't get caught.

24:28.820 --> 24:30.150
I think it's about time.

24:30.420 --> 24:31.480
Let's get started.

24:45.140 --> 24:46.290
Today,

24:46.290 --> 24:48.580
to send off Lord Fan and Lord Tian

24:48.580 --> 24:51.000
as they take up their posts in Jing City,

24:51.380 --> 24:54.180
an official farewell ceremony
has been arranged.

24:54.940 --> 24:55.600
Begin.

25:03.390 --> 25:05.420
In the fifth month
of the year of Bingshen,

25:05.420 --> 25:08.240
we pay homage to our ancestors
and successive generations of governors.

25:08.240 --> 25:10.300
Please perform the following rites:

25:30.120 --> 25:31.920
offer the Qi jade to Heaven,

25:32.050 --> 25:33.970
and the 9 clans are brought forth
in succession.

25:33.970 --> 25:34.730
Bow.

25:44.600 --> 25:46.440
Offer the yellow jade to Earth,

25:46.470 --> 25:48.730
and pillars stand firm
through generations.

25:48.730 --> 25:49.840
Bow.

25:55.660 --> 25:58.920
Ancestors of the Nine Cities,
please bless our territory.

25:59.060 --> 25:59.940
Bow.

26:01.510 --> 26:02.380
Gao Ran.

26:03.730 --> 26:04.420
Gao Ran?

26:06.970 --> 26:07.430
Gao Ran.

26:07.990 --> 26:09.320
Why are you ignoring me?

26:10.050 --> 26:11.690
I didn't hear you. I'm here.

26:14.580 --> 26:15.920
You're wearing a headband today?

26:15.920 --> 26:16.720
You mean this?

26:18.730 --> 26:20.390
It's a kind of amulet, I guess.

26:21.290 --> 26:22.420
An amulet?

26:23.820 --> 26:25.420
Didn't you

26:25.420 --> 26:27.260
ask me for an amulet before?

26:27.290 --> 26:29.330
Now that you're wearing this,

26:29.420 --> 26:30.770
what about mine?

26:30.770 --> 26:32.150
What should I do with this then?

26:32.150 --> 26:33.460
Well, this was

26:33.490 --> 26:34.530
specially bestowed by His Excellency.

26:34.530 --> 26:36.290
I couldn't really refuse it. But yours—

26:36.290 --> 26:37.500
I'll wear it as well.

26:37.580 --> 26:38.300
Together.

26:39.050 --> 26:41.210
Specially bestowed by His Excellency, huh?

26:41.210 --> 26:42.340
That's more like it.

26:42.420 --> 26:42.970
But

26:42.970 --> 26:44.620
even if you have 2 amulets now,

26:44.620 --> 26:45.860
you still can't let your guard down.

26:45.860 --> 26:47.420
You need to stay safe, okay?

26:47.420 --> 26:49.420
Just relax and put your mind at ease.

26:51.620 --> 26:52.530
Why do you

26:52.690 --> 26:55.010
seem a bit strange today?

26:56.010 --> 26:56.540
Strange?

26:57.910 --> 26:58.840
I don't think so.

26:58.870 --> 26:59.350
Come on.

26:59.790 --> 27:00.870
You know what?

27:01.170 --> 27:02.820
Our plan for Jing City

27:02.840 --> 27:04.240
is very well thought out.

27:05.050 --> 27:06.290
So don't worry at all.

27:08.070 --> 27:09.940
While I'm away,

27:09.960 --> 27:12.200
just keep a close eye on His Excellency.

27:24.730 --> 27:26.900
Then does that count as
me doing you a favor?

27:26.900 --> 27:27.940
Of course it does.

27:28.590 --> 27:31.220
Because your Gao Ran will be fine.

27:34.770 --> 27:36.680
My Gao Ran?

27:38.440 --> 27:40.010
Then rest assured.

27:40.040 --> 27:42.840
I'll definitely take good care of
His Excellency.

27:43.360 --> 27:44.090
I'm leaving.

27:53.530 --> 27:54.140
Perfect.

28:00.620 --> 28:01.750
Ceremony finished.

28:02.770 --> 28:05.430
-God bless Nine Cities.
-God bless Nine Cities.

28:27.790 --> 28:28.790
Your Excellency.

28:29.010 --> 28:30.770
Thank you for the farewell ceremony.

28:30.770 --> 28:31.770
Right now, I

28:32.110 --> 28:34.170
feel completely filled with energy.

28:36.250 --> 28:38.860
From now on, I'll treat every
newly appointed official

28:38.860 --> 28:40.580
with equal care and respect.

28:42.690 --> 28:45.580
Your Excellency truly loves your officials
and cares for the people,

28:45.580 --> 28:47.710
with the welfare of the realm at heart.

28:49.860 --> 28:50.450
You...

28:54.710 --> 28:56.710
Please mind your manners.

29:03.870 --> 29:04.660
Okay.

29:07.620 --> 29:09.100
By the way, Your Excellency,

29:09.100 --> 29:12.810
I noticed you and Gao Ran are both
wearing this on your foreheads.

29:13.220 --> 29:14.220
What is this?

29:14.790 --> 29:15.900
This is

29:16.200 --> 29:19.180
an amulet presented by the Ping family
during the Autumn Moon Festival.

29:19.180 --> 29:21.310
I thought it looked good on Gao Ran too,

29:21.860 --> 29:23.080
so I gave him a pair.

29:23.310 --> 29:24.030
That's all.

29:24.660 --> 29:25.420
An amulet?

29:27.180 --> 29:29.450
Well, since Gao Ran is coming with us
to Jing City,

29:29.450 --> 29:31.650
it makes sense for him to wear an amulet.

29:31.860 --> 29:33.750
But do you have to be so cautious

29:33.970 --> 29:35.210
in Ling'an too?

29:36.100 --> 29:37.300
I think it looks nice.

29:38.980 --> 29:40.540
It really suits my style.

29:42.810 --> 29:43.880
I see.

29:47.290 --> 29:48.950
I'll wait for you to come back.

29:50.590 --> 29:52.120
Take care of yourself, too.

30:09.250 --> 30:10.210
Fan Yun?

30:11.530 --> 30:12.290
Yes?

30:13.450 --> 30:15.010
Why is he traveling with us?

30:16.530 --> 30:18.530
You mean Second Young Master Zheng?

30:18.580 --> 30:21.620
He suggested a few days ago
that the two groups travel together.

30:21.620 --> 30:22.810
And I figured

30:22.920 --> 30:25.580
since he's relatively familiar
with the route to Jing City,

30:25.580 --> 30:28.280
it'd be nice to have someone
to look out for each other along the way.

30:28.280 --> 30:29.610
Look out for each other?

30:30.490 --> 30:31.410
I think

30:31.690 --> 30:32.910
it's more like an annoyance.

30:32.910 --> 30:33.950
Annoyance?

30:35.010 --> 30:36.210
What annoyance?

30:37.350 --> 30:38.680
I mean,

30:38.710 --> 30:40.770
we appreciate your kind intentions,
Second Young Master Zheng.

30:40.770 --> 30:42.520
It's just the more people we travel with,

30:42.520 --> 30:44.320
the more we stand out as a target.

30:44.340 --> 30:46.270
Isn't that a bit too ostentatious?

30:46.390 --> 30:48.820
It's true that we shouldn't draw attention
to ourselves on a long journey.

30:48.820 --> 30:50.820
But given this is a trip to Jing City,

30:50.860 --> 30:51.900
our Zheng family banner

30:51.900 --> 30:53.450
is the best protection.

30:53.940 --> 30:55.940
Lord Gao, you're worrying too much.

31:05.860 --> 31:06.290
Thank you.

31:06.290 --> 31:06.900
Hold on.

31:07.830 --> 31:09.550
Why is there no meat at all?

31:09.580 --> 31:10.860
The harvest wasn't good this year.

31:10.860 --> 31:12.900
All the chickens, ducks and fish
have been sent to Ling'an.

31:12.900 --> 31:14.450
Apologies for the poor hospitality.

31:14.450 --> 31:15.310
It's all right.

31:21.690 --> 31:22.340
Gao Ran.

31:23.660 --> 31:25.190
What do you want to say to me?

31:26.970 --> 31:28.060
I just wanted to say

31:28.510 --> 31:29.660
that Dad's cooking

31:29.680 --> 31:31.160
was way worse than this,

31:31.190 --> 31:32.650
yet you could bear with it.

31:32.690 --> 31:34.590
You must be too used to the good life now.

31:34.590 --> 31:35.790
Just go ahead and eat.

31:37.770 --> 31:38.940
Second Young Master Zheng,

31:38.940 --> 31:40.050
can you get used to the taste?

31:40.050 --> 31:41.180
It's just everyday food.

31:41.180 --> 31:42.840
What's there not to be used to?

31:48.050 --> 31:49.400
Still, I hope that

31:49.660 --> 31:52.490
in the future, people can eat meat
freely in big bites,

31:52.490 --> 31:55.950
and won't have to rely on
pickled vegetables to get by anymore.

31:58.050 --> 31:59.780
These are pickled vegetables?

32:01.100 --> 32:01.650
Yes.

32:04.690 --> 32:06.140
What's wrong with you, Gao Ran?

32:06.140 --> 32:07.940
You don't even recognize these?

32:08.550 --> 32:09.480
It's delicious.

32:09.980 --> 32:10.640
Delicious.

32:11.250 --> 32:12.650
Since it's so delicious,

32:13.490 --> 32:14.770
you should eat more.

32:16.050 --> 32:16.730
Eat more.

32:17.140 --> 32:18.200
Thank you, Fan Yun.

32:24.140 --> 32:25.210
What's going on?

32:25.710 --> 32:26.760
We're moving.

32:27.820 --> 32:29.580
-Mayor Zheng.
-Mayor Zheng.

32:31.620 --> 32:32.690
Why did you two come

32:32.690 --> 32:34.690
without giving me a notice in advance?

32:34.690 --> 32:35.340
Well...

32:35.340 --> 32:37.180
His Excellency just issued an oral decree,

32:37.180 --> 32:39.180
ordering the two of us to come here.

32:39.860 --> 32:41.260
There's another decree?

32:42.100 --> 32:43.050
That's right.

32:43.050 --> 32:46.690
In recognition of the heroic sacrifices
of your entire Zheng family,

32:46.690 --> 32:49.140
and in light of
the upcoming election for clan leader,

32:49.140 --> 32:51.270
His Excellency has hereby proclaimed

32:52.100 --> 32:53.950
that the new Zheng clan leader

32:54.210 --> 32:56.610
may directly inherit your military merits

32:56.660 --> 32:59.410
and be granted
the rank of Third-Rank General.

33:01.250 --> 33:02.530
The new clan leader

33:03.660 --> 33:04.490
will

33:09.100 --> 33:11.350
be granted the rank of Third-Rank General?

33:11.350 --> 33:13.480
I think this is actually great news.

33:15.530 --> 33:16.660
Just think about it—

33:16.670 --> 33:18.770
we've been working hard
for most of our lives,

33:18.770 --> 33:21.380
and isn't it all
for the sake of a happy retirement?

33:21.380 --> 33:22.320
Right?

33:22.670 --> 33:23.720
If you ask me,

33:23.820 --> 33:26.190
you shouldn't go to Jing City

33:26.420 --> 33:28.680
and meddle in the clan leader's affairs.

33:28.940 --> 33:30.900
Let's stay in Ling'an together

33:30.900 --> 33:33.210
and enjoy our retirement, shall we?

33:35.290 --> 33:37.290
Well, Mayor Zheng,

33:37.290 --> 33:38.430
His Excellency's intention

33:38.430 --> 33:40.980
is to help the Nine Cities
take on a new look.

33:41.640 --> 33:42.290
Look,

33:42.340 --> 33:43.690
if we old folks can just

33:43.690 --> 33:47.180
live a free and unrestrained life—
how carefree is that?

33:48.210 --> 33:50.490
Zheng the Second, stop dithering.

33:50.490 --> 33:52.150
J-Just give us a clear answer.

33:57.030 --> 33:59.940
The Zheng family is facing
a leadership vacuum.

34:00.820 --> 34:01.770
If I don't go back now,

34:01.770 --> 34:04.180
it'll be left to
my grandchildren's generation.

34:04.180 --> 34:06.510
They lack experience and are still young.

34:06.900 --> 34:07.940
I have to go back to Jing City

34:07.940 --> 34:09.260
to take charge of the overall situation
for them.

34:09.260 --> 34:11.940
Please return the detained Zheng's Army

34:12.780 --> 34:13.570
to me.

34:16.190 --> 34:16.800
What?

34:17.159 --> 34:18.120
Detained?

34:18.480 --> 34:19.090
Zhao.

34:19.940 --> 34:20.969
You know about this?

34:20.969 --> 34:22.300
I had absolutely no idea.

34:22.300 --> 34:24.900
Wait, there's no such thing
as being detained.

34:25.370 --> 34:27.080
Our Ling'an is a place of
outstanding people and beautiful scenery,

34:27.080 --> 34:28.320
and the land and climate are nurturing.

34:28.320 --> 34:31.320
Anyone who comes here
never wants to leave.

34:31.380 --> 34:32.969
Your army has also

34:32.969 --> 34:34.900
gotten along very well with
Gao Ran and Commander Wei

34:34.900 --> 34:37.050
since they arrived here.

34:37.050 --> 34:38.010
And none of them wants to leave.

34:38.010 --> 34:39.090
Yes. That's right.

34:39.380 --> 34:40.650
Mayor Zheng,

34:41.739 --> 34:43.650
with so many people staying here,

34:43.650 --> 34:45.340
if you're not here to watch over them,

34:45.340 --> 34:47.570
we won't feel at ease.

34:47.570 --> 34:48.610
Exactly.

34:49.900 --> 34:51.050
You guys...

34:55.940 --> 34:57.150
What does he mean?

34:57.700 --> 34:59.300
Seems like he's not leaving.

35:10.570 --> 35:11.610
So,

35:11.610 --> 35:13.860
this is your first time
sleeping in the wild?

35:13.860 --> 35:14.610
Yes.

35:17.170 --> 35:18.010
If we go to

35:18.010 --> 35:20.260
a post house or an inn
at a time like this,

35:20.260 --> 35:21.720
we'll easily be targeted.

35:22.550 --> 35:24.760
Let's just have a simple meal tonight.

35:28.450 --> 35:30.220
Fan Yun, the soup is boiling.

35:30.700 --> 35:31.340
Okay.

35:31.860 --> 35:33.260
We can start cooking the vegetables.

35:33.260 --> 35:33.930
Here.

35:33.950 --> 35:35.130
The vegetables have been washed.

35:35.130 --> 35:35.700
Suyin,

35:36.130 --> 35:36.590
come on.

35:36.970 --> 35:38.300
Give me the vegetables.

35:39.490 --> 35:40.170
Let me do it.

35:41.600 --> 35:42.460
It's okay, I...

35:42.490 --> 35:44.200
Let me do it, Fan Yun.

35:44.570 --> 35:45.610
We've been on the road all day.

35:45.610 --> 35:46.870
You must be exhausted.

35:47.130 --> 35:49.170
I-I'm not really tired.

35:51.780 --> 35:52.380
Come on.

35:53.970 --> 35:56.570
Zheng Xian, let's go pick
some wild vegetables.

35:56.570 --> 35:58.260
It'll be ready soon.

36:17.830 --> 36:18.830
Show yourselves.

36:29.280 --> 36:30.540
How dare you follow me?

36:30.770 --> 36:32.830
Do you have a death wish or something?

36:39.780 --> 36:40.510
Right,

36:41.340 --> 36:43.070
you can help me with something.

36:43.900 --> 36:44.960
Careful, it's hot.

36:45.010 --> 36:45.700
Okay.

36:49.530 --> 36:50.550
Add a bit more firewood.

36:50.550 --> 36:51.130
Okay.

37:00.240 --> 37:01.110
Fish?

37:01.170 --> 37:01.860
For you.

37:04.170 --> 37:05.430
Where did you get this?

37:05.820 --> 37:08.080
Thank you for letting me travel with you.

37:10.260 --> 37:11.340
We have fish to eat.

37:11.340 --> 37:13.540
I never agreed to let you travel with us.

37:17.380 --> 37:19.260
What happened to those
who were following us?

37:19.260 --> 37:20.740
We've driven them all off.

37:20.970 --> 37:22.630
Things should be fine for now.

37:24.220 --> 37:25.940
What's bound to happen will happen.

37:25.940 --> 37:26.610
It's actually understandable.

37:26.610 --> 37:28.450
After all, Jing City is expecting
a new gate commander.

37:28.450 --> 37:30.610
Those people won't have it easy either.

37:30.610 --> 37:33.270
I'm afraid the road ahead
will only get tougher.

37:34.650 --> 37:36.450
Master Chief Military Officer.

37:38.920 --> 37:40.650
Fan Yun, rest assured.

37:41.090 --> 37:41.880
To protect you,

37:41.880 --> 37:43.510
I'm willing to pay any price.

37:45.260 --> 37:45.930
Okay.

37:47.650 --> 37:48.650
I see.

37:48.650 --> 37:51.010
Then... you two talk.

37:51.340 --> 37:52.260
I'll go over there and check on

37:52.260 --> 37:53.300
Tian Xing and Suyin.

37:53.300 --> 37:54.050
Be careful.

38:48.220 --> 38:50.020
What's wrong, Your Excellency?

38:50.820 --> 38:52.080
Why are today's dishes

38:52.490 --> 38:53.700
so salty?

38:54.450 --> 38:56.090
Your Excellency, every dish was

38:56.090 --> 38:57.370
made according to your taste.

38:57.370 --> 38:59.070
If you prefer a lighter taste today,

38:59.070 --> 39:01.070
I'll go change it for you right away.

39:01.090 --> 39:01.820
No need.

39:03.050 --> 39:05.420
Since they were made
according to my taste,

39:05.420 --> 39:06.620
let's not waste them.

39:06.740 --> 39:07.740
Your Excellency.

39:11.490 --> 39:12.430
Forget it, forget it.

39:12.430 --> 39:14.290
I was wondering why it's so salty.

39:14.340 --> 39:15.650
How could anyone eat it anyway?

39:15.650 --> 39:16.650
Take it away.

39:28.450 --> 39:29.340
These

39:29.340 --> 39:31.140
are some pastries I made myself.

39:31.170 --> 39:32.050
I thought

39:32.050 --> 39:34.610
you might be tired of the food here,

39:34.610 --> 39:37.010
so I brought you something different
for a change. Try it.

39:37.010 --> 39:39.270
You've certainly become more sensible.

39:51.330 --> 39:52.210
How is it?

39:52.300 --> 39:53.380
A gift full of sincerity

39:53.380 --> 39:54.530
really is different.

39:54.530 --> 39:55.990
Even a picky eater like him

39:56.300 --> 39:57.230
can't resist it.

40:00.680 --> 40:02.640
What's this pastry made of?

40:02.700 --> 40:03.260
This is

40:03.260 --> 40:04.530
our Gao City's specialty—

40:04.530 --> 40:05.700
Egg and Pomelo Cake.

40:08.540 --> 40:09.060
Pom...

40:09.560 --> 40:10.390
Pomelo?

40:12.260 --> 40:13.340
What's wrong, Your Excellency?

40:13.340 --> 40:14.220
Didn't you say

40:14.220 --> 40:16.220
you liked our Gao City's pomelo?

40:16.220 --> 40:17.780
I thought I'd make more for you.

40:17.780 --> 40:19.700
Don't let the small size of
this plate fool you—

40:19.700 --> 40:22.090
I squeezed a whole pomelo into it.

40:22.490 --> 40:23.050
This...

40:25.090 --> 40:25.940
What's wrong?

40:26.740 --> 40:27.610
Is it not good?

40:28.740 --> 40:30.670
Your Excellency, what's going on?

40:34.090 --> 40:34.860
I'm fine.

40:36.280 --> 40:37.950
Quick, call Lord Jiang over.

40:37.970 --> 40:38.860
-Okay.
-I can't breathe.

40:38.860 --> 40:39.780
I'm on my way.

40:39.780 --> 40:40.530
I... I'll go.

40:40.530 --> 40:41.530
No, I'll go.

40:41.750 --> 40:43.350
I'm faster than you. I'll go.

40:49.170 --> 40:50.420
There's less than
half a day's journey left

40:50.420 --> 40:51.380
to Jing City.

40:51.820 --> 40:53.120
Let's move a bit faster

40:53.310 --> 40:54.970
and try to arrive before dark.

40:56.020 --> 40:56.750
Here.

40:59.170 --> 40:59.820
Thank you.

41:00.450 --> 41:01.490
Take a rest first.

41:03.730 --> 41:04.460
Shi.

41:05.700 --> 41:06.330
Come here.

41:11.530 --> 41:13.490
Now that the Gate Commander Residence
has been burned down,

41:13.490 --> 41:16.130
Brother probably wouldn't
have the mood to repair it.

41:16.130 --> 41:18.380
Where will Lady Fan Yun and her party stay

41:18.380 --> 41:19.780
once they enter the city?

41:20.740 --> 41:21.940
Jing City is such a large city.

41:21.940 --> 41:22.900
Surely there won't be a shortage of places

41:22.900 --> 41:24.900
for just a few of them to stay, right?

41:25.300 --> 41:26.420
How about

41:26.420 --> 41:28.300
the two of us enter the city first

41:28.300 --> 41:30.220
and arrange accommodations for them?

41:30.220 --> 41:31.940
Otherwise, we'll be scrambling
at the last minute,

41:31.940 --> 41:35.090
and it might look like our Zheng family
is neglecting the gate commander.

41:35.090 --> 41:36.220
You're actually right.

41:36.220 --> 41:37.880
We should prepare in advance.

41:40.010 --> 41:41.900
Jing City is now filled with
undercurrents.

41:41.900 --> 41:43.700
It's no longer what it used to be.

41:43.940 --> 41:45.700
There might very well be people
inside the city

41:45.700 --> 41:47.090
plotting to harm the new gate commander

41:47.090 --> 41:48.530
and preparing a breakaway faction.

41:48.530 --> 41:50.300
Shi, that's not what I meant.

41:51.570 --> 41:53.770
We should always prepare for the worst.

41:55.570 --> 41:56.380
Fan Yun.

41:58.700 --> 42:00.300
I'll wait for you in the city.

42:03.700 --> 42:04.220
Okay.

42:07.610 --> 42:09.010
Get ready to hit the road.

42:30.680 --> 42:33.540
He said something about
preparing for the worst...

42:39.570 --> 42:40.900
What are you looking at?

42:40.940 --> 42:43.140
Are you that reluctant to part with him?

42:43.880 --> 42:44.840
-Keep looking then.
-I…

42:44.840 --> 42:47.770
He won't come back no matter
how long you look anyway.

42:49.170 --> 42:50.130
He...

42:50.570 --> 42:51.650
He's already come back.

42:51.650 --> 42:52.740
No way...

42:55.530 --> 42:57.060
Second Young Master Zheng,

42:57.120 --> 42:58.340
why did you turn back?

42:58.340 --> 42:59.340
Being the gate commander of Jing City

42:59.340 --> 43:01.020
is not like being one anywhere else.

43:01.020 --> 43:02.130
The road ahead is dangerous.

43:02.130 --> 43:04.060
Please take good care of yourself.

43:11.120 --> 43:12.830
Anything else you want to say?

43:14.050 --> 43:15.090
You can leave now.

43:18.300 --> 43:19.960
I'll wait for you in Jing City.

43:22.020 --> 43:23.830
-W-Who asked you to wait?
-Okay.

43:31.260 --> 43:32.150
Ridiculous.

43:32.340 --> 43:33.000
This guy...

43:33.350 --> 43:35.440
He's really such a pain. What a pain.

43:37.220 --> 43:37.970
Gao Ran?

43:38.700 --> 43:39.220
Come on.

43:39.490 --> 43:40.410
Come sit.

43:41.300 --> 43:42.340
Sit here.

43:43.010 --> 43:43.740
Come on.

44:08.300 --> 44:10.340
You don't have a fever or anything.

44:10.780 --> 44:12.570
Why have you been acting so weird
these past few days,

44:12.570 --> 44:15.010
targeting that Second Young Master Zheng
all the time?

44:15.010 --> 44:16.810
You don't usually act like this.

44:16.920 --> 44:17.730
I...

44:20.860 --> 44:21.860
I...

44:26.760 --> 44:27.570
I know.

44:28.010 --> 44:29.300
You know?

44:31.450 --> 44:33.440
You must have

44:33.610 --> 44:35.130
spent too much time with that Miss Wei,

44:35.130 --> 44:37.010
so you've become as quirky as her.

44:38.010 --> 44:39.780
Have you two already...

44:40.820 --> 44:41.640
Yes...

44:41.860 --> 44:42.770
No, it's not like that.

44:42.770 --> 44:43.880
He said it himself

44:43.970 --> 44:45.170
that the Zheng family is plotting

44:45.170 --> 44:46.610
to harm the new gate commander.

44:46.610 --> 44:48.050
He's a member of the Zheng family
after all.

44:48.050 --> 44:51.170
It's better to be safe than sorry.
